{
  "text": "In conditions of similar resolutions (LR), the activations detected in our study recover only a part of the activations described by the meta-analyses [CITATION_1] 29] , in particular no activation was found in left amygdala, left lateral OFC, and right insula. A lack of sensitivity undoubtedly explains the low inter-study reproducibility reported in the meta-analyses and justifies using the possibly more sensitive conditions of HR.",
